      "content": "**Structural alerts / motifs**\n- **Classic hERG pharmacophore pattern present:** **basic cationic center + two hydrophobic/aromatic groups** at an appropriate separation.\n- Not a piperidine/terfenadine per se, but **functionally similar topology** (cationic center flanked by aryl groups with flexible spacers).",
